{"title":"2020-06-02","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><p>通常交換でまさかの連続キラ。しかもサイホーンは <g-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"100\" fallback-src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f4af.png\">💯</g-emoji></p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-06-02/20200602-215538-Screenshot_20200602-215538.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-06-02/20200602-215538-Screenshot_20200602-215538.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2020/2020-06-02/20200602-215541-Screenshot_20200602-215541.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-06-02/20200602-215541-Screenshot_20200602-215541.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>レシラムよりゼクロム派なんだよな。黒かっこいい。その時期に全力出せるか否か… そして、金沢駅前出るの、やっぱり今はすげぇ気になるんだよな。どこでやればいいんだろ？</p>\n<p>地域の情報がほぼない…</p>\n<hr>\n<p>ポケモンメンテナンスか。</p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記,つぶやき,雑記帳","updated":"2020-06-02T18:53:47","published":"2020-06-02T18:53:47"}